like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"面皮又薄，一年又轉左幾份工，失業左幾個月"},{"pid":"07e2c0016b927d2a8a18a20bd155cf7922bcf02a","tid":828542,"uid":49215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"咁廢都有老婆？"},{"pid":"52efb9b47b5ad36cea74423367535cd38f10c157","tid":828542,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:35:12.000Z","msg":"整體同你一樣 不過條命生得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時都覺得自己好冇用，所有野都係人地比我，冇一樣係真係自己成功得到，份人又懶，決定要做又拖到冇時間做唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb3d43fb30f52c67a3a778d3860eedceab3cbe5","tid":828542,"uid":184378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e2c0016b927d2a8a18a20bd155cf7922bcf02a","tid":828542,"uid":49215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"咁廢都有老婆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:35:14.000Z","msg":"我都唔知"},{"pid":"488260fbb940cfcf3973118eb6e373518288cf44","tid":828542,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edb3d43fb30f52c67a3a778d3860eedceab3cbe5","tid":828542,"uid":184378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e2c0016b927d2a8a18a20bd155cf7922bcf02a","tid":828542,"uid":49215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"咁廢都有老婆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:35:14.000Z","msg":"我都唔知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:36:02.000Z","msg":"咁你老婆都幾好"},{"pid":"9c4e4c8dfb0687fb970421e5b7c21890c08893f2","tid":828542,"uid":208713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"其實你有冇覺得自己唔應該做人老公？"},{"pid":"039ac820f59a2c01f4e7f7e049b7fce2bc3d9b6f","tid":828542,"uid":113021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5155442b838755aae35d3bb5ecb486230cc3e9aa","tid":828542,"uid":184378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"面皮又薄，一年又轉左幾份工，失業左幾個月"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:36:54.000Z","msg":"你做開咩工既先?<br />\n面皮薄真係好蝕底<br />\n我以前都係咁<br />\n但逼逼下就愈黎愈放膽<br />\n<br />\n我覺得面皮薄源自於欠缺自信<br />\n當你係某個area 好了得既時候，知道人地駁你唔到<br />\n講野就會愈黎愈大膽 甚至愈黎愈串<br />\n所以你份份工都做唔長既話，永遠都係門外漢<br />\n係惡性循環黎"},{"pid":"fcef6c69d55d48c096267023e16639707a75cdf7","tid":828542,"uid":184378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c4e4c8dfb0687fb970421e5b7c21890c08893f2","tid":828542,"uid":208713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:36:49.000Z","msg":"其實你有冇覺得自己唔應該做人老公？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T18:37:21.000Z","msg":"我害左人地個女 ，又係埋自己個仔"}]}